            "width": 560,
            "content": "## Fetch & Split\nFetches today's Austrian tenders from TED API and splits the `notices` array into individual items.\n\n⚠️ Date uses `$now.toFormat('yyyyMMdd')` — always dynamic, no duplicates."
          },
          "typeVersion": 1
        },
